data.description: This stunning ranch-style home boasts a spacious open floor plan that's perfect for modern living. With an expansive layout, this property offers a seamless flow from room to room, creating a welcoming and inviting atmosphere. The heart of the home is the generously sized living area, flooded with natural light from large windows, creating a warm and vibrant ambiance.  But the charm doesn't end there. This home also features a fully finished basement, providing even more living space for relaxation, entertainment, or hobbies. The possibilities are endless, from a cozy family room to a home gym, office, or guest quarters.  Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, the property offers privacy and convenience, making it an ideal retreat. Step outside to enjoy a spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor activities or gatherings. The ranch-style design ensures accessibility and comfort for residents of all ages.  Overall, this property combines the best of open, contemporary living with the practicality of a ranch-style layout and the added bonus of a finished basement. It's a unique and inviting space ready to be transformed into your dream home. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!   BATVAI
